        "message": "=Dear {{ $('Get row(s) in sheet').item.json['Employer Contact'] }},\n\nI hope this email finds you well.\n\nWe are writing to confirm the placement of our student {{ $('Get row(s) in sheet').item.json['Student Name'] }} at {{ $('Get row(s) in sheet').item.json['Employer'] }}.\n\nCould you please confirm the following:\n1. The student is attending their placement as expected\n2. You are happy with their performance so far\n3. You are able to complete and sign the employer section of their placement form\n\nPlease simply reply to this email to confirm.\n\nKind regards,\nWIC Placement Team\nWaltham International College, Barking",
        "options": {
          "appendAttribution": false,
          "senderName": "WIC Placement Team"
        }
