              "content": "=You are the placement office at Waltham International College (WIC) in Barking, London.\n\nWrite a friendly but firm reminder email to a student who has NOT returned their placement form.\n\nStudent Name: {{ $json['Student Name'] }}\nEmployer: {{ $json['Employer'] }}\nForm originally sent: {{ $json['Date Sent'] }}\n\nThe email should:\n- Be warm but make clear this is urgent\n- Remind them the deadline is approaching\n- Mention failure to return may affect course completion\n- Be under 120 words\n\nEnd with:\nKind regards,\nWIC Placement Team\n\nReturn only the email body. No subject line."
            }
          ]
